# HackTheEast – Agent Context

## Target tracks (one product, three prizes)

### OAX Foundation AI EdTech Platform (HKD 15,000)
**Problem:** Content overload in fast-moving fields (AI, crypto, geopolitics) — impossible to filter and absorb relevant material.
**Criteria:** Real-world learner impact · Timesaving & learning acceleration · Personalisation · Creative thinking

### MiniMax Creative Usage (HKD 15,000)
**Must use:** MiniMax API (LLM, video, audio, music). Multiple MiniMax tools working together for creative experiences.
**Our use:** Tutorial generation (LLM scripts + video + speech + music), news illustration (trending events → video + score).

### RevisionDojo Future of Learning (HKD 15,000)
**Focus:** AI-powered learning: feedback, personalisation, assessment, mastery for strong + struggling learners.
**Our use:** 3–5 step tutorials with completion tracking, progress, and OAX badges.

---

**Our solution — LearnPulse:** AI-powered EdTech platform that uses Exa AI for content discovery, MiniMax for rich tutorial/media generation, and a RevisionDojo-style completion system with badges. "Catch me up" summarises what changed in your tracked domains.

**Key APIs:** Exa AI (semantic search), MiniMax (M2.5 LLM, Hailuo video, Music 2.5, Speech 2.8), Supabase (data).

